fields.name: Big Bang
fields.description: Capturing the explosive beauty of creation, the Big Bang watch features a dynamic design that mimics the universe's birth. With a dial that sparkles with a galaxy pattern, it's a piece of cosmic art.

fields.name: Supernova
fields.description: Illuminating the cosmos, the Supernova watch dazzles with a design inspired by the brilliant light of a star's explosive end. Its dial glows, embodying the power and beauty of a supernova.

fields.name: Venus
fields.description: Echoing the allure of the morning star, the Venus watch combines elegance with brilliance. With a rose gold finish and a dial that captures Venus' glow, it's a watch that enchants.

fields.name: Mars
fields.description: Inspired by the red planet, the Mars watch features a robust design with a red dial and a durable case that mirrors Mars' rugged landscape. It's a watch for the adventurous spirit.

fields.name: Saturn
fields.description: Encircling your wrist like Saturn's rings, this watch features a unique ring design around the dial. With a striking resemblance to Saturn, it's a celestial marvel.

fields.name: Uranus
fields.description: Reflecting Uranus' icy blue, this watch features a cool blue dial and a sleek, modern design. It's a watch that combines mystery with elegance.

fields.name: Planet-X
fields.description: For the explorers of the unknown, the Planet-X watch embodies the mystery of the unseen. With a design that suggests the enigmatic, this watch is a tribute to the worlds beyond.

fields.name: Uranus
fields.description: Reflecting Uranus' icy blue, this watch features a cool blue dial and a sleek, modern design. It's a watch that combines mystery with elegance.

fields.name: Planet-X
fields.description: For the explorers of the unknown, the Planet-X watch embodies the mystery of the unseen. With a design that suggests the enigmatic, this watch is a tribute to the worlds beyond.

fields.name: Neptune
fields.description: Dive into the depths of the cosmos with the Neptune watch, featuring a deep blue dial and silver accents that mirror the distant planet's mystique and allure.

fields.name: Jupiter
fields.description: Embrace the majesty of the solar system's largest planet with the Jupiter watch. Its swirling patterns and striking colors are reminiscent of Jupiter's famous Great Red Spot.

fields.name: Mercury
fields.description: Inspired by the swift movement of Mercury around the sun, this watch features a sleek, metallic design. It's the perfect blend of speed and style.

fields.name: Luna Astro
fields.description: The Luna Astro watch pays homage to the moon's phases with a dial that changes appearance with time, mirroring the lunar cycle. It's a celestial wonder on your wrist.

fields.name: Phobos
fields.description: Named after Mars' moon, the Phobos watch is bold and striking, featuring a dark, mysterious dial with red accents that hint at its Martian inspiration.

fields.name: Deimos
fields.description: Complementing its sibling, the Deimos watch captures the essence of the farther of Mars' two moons. It features a sleek, dark design with subtle hints of red.
